N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 5.30 - Ordering from lists

State Regulations

An employer may employ security officers and supervisory
security officers from his regular and extra security officer lists filed with
the commission in accordance with sections 5.35 through
5.41
of this Part, inclusive. Notes
